  "detailed_description": "It's a retro western styled, maze racing game with progressive difficulty levels, that starts from easy to more complex.<br />\r\nYou are alone in the game. it's a single player game. But with the option to save multiple user profiles.<br />\r\nThe ambiance in the game has 30 western style music's  \"check the music in the video\", with a retro western outdoor architecture style.<br />\r\nAs the name indicates you should play the levels many times to get better record times.<br />\r\nIt's a 50 level game to find the checkpoints and do the needed laps to the finish line. Good luck!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*Update August 2023 - Added audio sound fx",
